      /**
       * Determine whether a given method should be ignored, according to various jackson annotations for that purpose,
       * <br>
       * e.g. {@code JsonBackReference}, {@code JsonIgnore}, {@code JsonIgnoreType}, {@code JsonIgnoreProperties}
